reviewText: Good compilation of war films.  I was lacking a couple of the more obscure titles for my collection, this filled three of the gaps...for the right price.
European format, won't play in USA. worthless.
Had scratches...some movie did not play.

We have attempted to watch 2 of the movies so far with poor results.  Convoy had several dropouts and poor sound, but interesting pic so I tolerated it.
Commandos would start with poor qualty video and sound, then stopped playing all together.  I tried this on 3 different DVD players, with similar results.  Other DVDs worked fine.
Will check rest and see if same results.
